wherein said at least a front lighting unit is tiltable, being capable of being adjusted to enhance visibility, and each lighting unit has a height of at least about ¾ inch, and approximate width of 1½ inches and a depth of at least about ¾ inch;
further comprising a mechanical interface made up of a bracket mount, or removable and adjustable closure of attachment to ensure universal usage for all types of strollers (different circumference of closures);
